  2.0.2.

*ilmbase-2.0.1 (23 Jul 2013)

  23 Jul 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +ilmbase-2.0.1.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  21 Mar 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> ilmbase-2.0.0.ebuild,
  +files/ilmbase-2.0.0-underlinking.patch:
  Link libIlmThread against $(PTHREAD_LIBS) from m4/threads.m4 wrt #462494 by
  Julian Ospald and Daniel Scharrer

  21 Mar 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> ilmbase-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Don't use ucontext.h from libc with this release of IlmBase wrt #461594 by
  Viktor Yu. Kovalskiy and Tupone Alfredo because of toolchain incompabilities.

  12 Mar 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> ilmbase-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Use subslot 0/10 based on SONAME.

